freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: With my 1st Pfizer shot in Jan I developed a knot at the injection site that was as big as 1/2 tennis ball. I still have a knot in that first arm. It is no longer uncomfortable but still there but about the size of a quarter. The 2nd Pfizer shot that I received 2/17/2021 has not produced any swelling or pain at all.
